    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Disclaimer</h2>The full story will be set in 6 chapters. The beta demo features chapter 1.<br>The beta version will not include voice overs or translations.<br>The music tracks are pre production demos, final production will start closer to the end of the development, once I'll have more or all the music written.<br>The UI and menus are fully functional, but not all fully designed.<br>Other than that everything else is polished to between 95%-100%.<br>Lastly, bugs may occur and we encourage you to report them if you catch them!<br><br>Mikey and Grover's Unexpected Adventures is a point and click adventure, featuring retro hand drawn pixel art and animations.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180790/extras/d8bdcdc65d81824be7e8616f7c3c4f87.apng?t=1722032539\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180790/extras/d8bdcdc65d81824be7e8616f7c3c4f87.poster.avif?t=1722032539\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=63 /></picture></span><br>Mikey is an ordinary kid who enjoys a good snack and really hates spiders. But above all else, he loves guitars!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180790/extras/9842b07b683dbb0a3561efe473404ee1.poster.avif?t=1722032539\" width=610 height=343 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180790/extras/9842b07b683dbb0a3561efe473404ee1.webm?t=1722032539\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>On his 12th birthday Mikey wished for his dream guitar, the Bender SG200.<br>But alas, Mikey’s wish did not come to pass.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180790/extras/a68dbb78e09886e1bb8d9a20760724f3.poster.avif?t=1722032539\" width=610 height=343 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180790/extras/a68dbb78e09886e1bb8d9a20760724f3.webm?t=1722032539\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>So, when Mikey learns from his uncle Chuck about the tales of hidden treasures in the lighthouse, he makes the responsible decision and drags his best bud Grover on a hunt for that long lost treasure.<br><br>Mikey will hear many different stories about the lighthouse, some of them are absolutely bananas. Or, are they?<br><br>The boys don’t really know what they’ll find over there, anything is possible, but they are ready and they are brave... No. That’s a very strong word... They are fearless... Wait, no, that’s not it either... They’ll somehow, with a little bit of luck, make it through a bunch of unexpected adventures.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180790/extras/e08854146e41b893600e8f892913e76e.apng?t=1722032539\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180790/extras/e08854146e41b893600e8f892913e76e.poster.avif?t=1722032539\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=63 /></picture></span><br>Talk to town's peoples and learn all about the tales of the lighthouse. Gather items, solve puzzles and make your way to that treasure!<br><br>The game is suitable for all ages and contains no foul language or violence.",
